Prepare Disks

Assuming installation disk is /dev/sda

Minimum requirements:

/dev/sda1	600MB	FAT32	EF00 (efi)	/boot
/dev/sda2	9GB	swap	linux-swap	swapon
/dev/sda3	20GB	ext4	root		/
/dev/sda4	30GB	ext4	home		/home

Formatting
mkfs.vfat	/dev/sda1
mkfs.swap	/dev/sda2
mkfs.ext4	/dev/sda3
mkfs.ext4	/dev/sda4

